title: Sex Pistols - Never Mind The Bullocks [AC3 5.1] [Bubanee]
description:
For more AC3 5.1 click on user name "Bubanee"

Never Mind the Bollocks, Here's the Sex Pistols is the first and only
studio album recorded by the Sex Pistols, a highly influential and controversial
English punk band. Fans and critics alike generally regard the album as an
extremely important record in the history of rock music, citing the lasting 
influence it has had on subsequent punk musicians and other musical genres 
that were influenced by such punk rock artists.

The album was released on 28 October 1977 on the Virgin Records label,
amid controversy arising from the use of the 
obscenity (in British English) "bollocks" in its title.
